{"tid":2186492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"舊作批評歐美社會曾讓習近平盛讚　法國經濟學家新書談及中共坐視不平等 在中國出版受阻","createTime":"2020-09-03T04:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T05:00:52.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf744044ce5031542f527aefcf42dd10d1b4c70d","tid":2186492,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:20:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200831/HF7L6DVYK5HCFFTKUZPPMGKYEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200831%2FHF7L6DVYK5HCFFTKUZPPMGKYEU%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=65a8e656\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200831%2FHF7L6DVYK5HCFFTKUZPPMGKYEU%2F&h=9fab19bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200831/HF7L6DVYK5HCFFTKUZPPMGKYEU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法國經濟學家皮凱提（Thomas Piketty）的巨著《21世紀資本論》批評當代資本主義與歐美社會不平等，2013年出版後紅遍全球，連中共總書記習近平都稱讚，還曾在2015年一場演說中利用該書來闡述馬克思主義最優秀。<br />\n<br />\n然而，皮凱提新書《資本與意識型態》擴大探討不平等的主題，在中國出版卻受阻，因為中方要求刪除所有涉及中國社會不平等的內容，皮凱提無法同意。<br />\n<br />\n香港《南華早報》報導，去年出版的《資本與意識型態》（Capital et Id&eacute;ologie），原本將由中信出版集團出中國版，但皮凱提透露，中信要求刪除書中所有中國不平等的內容，「我拒絕這些條件，因此目前看來，《資本與意識型態》不會在中國出版」。<br />\n<br />\n中信集團則回應稱，很榮幸曾與皮凱提合作《21世紀資本論》一書，至於新書的版權還在洽談中。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，在中國出版書籍，審查常是先決條件，因為中共對於出版、廣播電視、網路內容均嚴格控制。皮凱提的新書內容雖非針對中國，但有數頁談及中共坐視不平等加劇的情況，也提到人民收入與財富分配的官方資料極為稀缺，還觸及中國雖採社會主義政治體系，社會卻高度不平等。<br />\n<br />\n根據皮凱提在書中引述的數據，在1990年代初期，中國最富有的10%人口掌握的財富總值佔全國40%至50%，貧富不均程度低於瑞典；但到了2018年，此一數據卻上升至70%，與高度貧富不均的美國等國家近似。"},{"pid":"0685f3a7252592697735913ebc26095b8e72ced4","tid":2186492,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:25:58.000Z","msg":"前年佢先黎過香港<br />\n係教大講talk<br />\n上堂時個professor 仲叫我地聽佢個talk<br />\n講inequality <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yQRGCgjhU1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyQRGCgjhU1s&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=890b937c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yQRGCgjhU1s</a>"},{"pid":"cb9971c6b78a234160166426ffa76cd3cec0e923","tid":2186492,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0685f3a7252592697735913ebc26095b8e72ced4","tid":2186492,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:25:58.000Z","msg":"前年佢先黎過香港<br />\n係教大講talk<br />\n上堂時個professor 仲叫我地聽佢個talk<br />\n講inequality <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yQRGCgjhU1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyQRGCgjhU1s&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=890b937c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yQRGCgjhU1s</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:30:41.000Z","msg":"放心 入境處国安組會確保呢啲涉嫌違反港區国安法外部勢力人士入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91443fb015601079690bbec6e2745beee04e4849","tid":2186492,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb9971c6b78a234160166426ffa76cd3cec0e923","tid":2186492,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0685f3a7252592697735913ebc26095b8e72ced4","tid":2186492,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:25:58.000Z","msg":"前年佢先黎過香港<br />\n係教大講talk<br />\n上堂時個professor 仲叫我地聽佢個talk<br />\n講inequality <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yQRGCgjhU1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyQRGCgjhU1s&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=890b937c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yQRGCgjhU1s</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:30:41.000Z","msg":"放心 入境處国安組會確保呢啲涉嫌違反港區国安法外部勢力人士入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:00:52.000Z","msg":"本書變左做禁書"}]}